      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>吾何以知其然哉？以此。天下多忌諱，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>How do I know that it is so? By these facts: - In the kingdom the multiplication of prohibitive enactments increases the poverty of the people;</seg>
